- Number of lateral combs in nota: According 
Kaplin's
description (in Russian), the Turkmenian species has a lower number of combs in the pronotum (5 pairs), in the mesonotum (8-10 pairs) and in the metanotum (7-9 pairs), while the new species from Iran has respectively 9+10 combs, 14 pairs and 11 pairs of combs;
